* {{PropertyData|Samples|IntegerConstraint}}: Number of samples.
* {{PropertyData|Scale|Float}}: Scale (%). 0 for AutoScale.
* {{PropertyData|Shape|PartShape}}: Shape of comb plot.

{{TitleProperty|Surface}}

* {{PropertyData|Number|Integer}}: Number of surface samples.
* {{PropertyData|Orientation|Enumeration}}: Surface Comb Orientation.
** {{Value|U}} (default): ...
